title: Missing a vital cog in the wheel
text: Missing a vital cog in the wheel Sunday, 4 October 2015 (2 minutes ago) Absence of Mohammed Shami has reduced India’s bowling attack’s potency in the death overs. Four Killed In Tour Bus Collision On Seattle Bridge 00:53 Four people were killed and 15 critically injured on Thursday when an amphibious tour bus and a charter bus carrying foreign college students collided head-on on a Seattle bridge.
